<h1>Show Details by Article ID</h1>

<p>
  <strong>Title:</strong>
  <%= @article.title %>
</p>
 
<p>
  <strong>Text:</strong>
  <%= @article.text %>
</p>

<h3>Comments</h3>
<%= render @article.comments %>
<!-- This will now render the partial once for each comment that is in the @article.comments collection. As the render method iterates over the @article.comments collection, it assigns each comment to a local variable named the same as the partial, in this case comment which is then available in the partial for us to show.-->

<h3>Add a comment:</h3>
<%= render 'comments/form' %>

<button><%= link_to 'Back', articles_path %></button>  
<button><%= link_to 'Edit', edit_article_path(@article) %></button>